== Pre-requisites ==

This extension was tested with MediaWiki 1.6.7 and Mediawiki 1.8.2. 

== Installation ==

Get the source vi SVN. 

In your MediaWiki LocalSettings.php, add the following line some place
towards the bottom of the file:

 require_once("$IP/extensions/BlockTitles/BlockTitles.php");

== Configuration ==

Simply add any regular expressions you want to the variable $wgBlockTitlePatterns in BlockTitles.php. 
By default there are no set patterns.

